p: there and there be considered concerning the said Frank Burk together write the time and cause of this detention and that he have there detention, and that he have them and there the said writ. Dated May 27th 1875 J. R. Srier Judge Order Granting Writ of Habeaus Corpus Frank Burk vs. James J. Kenewortey Filed May 27 1875 James Dewy Clark By Benah Prerum, Deputy
